des:
So, Mr. Moose is a Canadian, eh. Like all Canadians he is very helpful, and he wants to help you be Canadian too. 
Mr. Moose will share great tips, eh, on how best to become a part of one the most awesome nationalities that starts with C and ends with “eh”.
